{"tid":810910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬斯克直播節目抽大麻🚬 或違反與空軍合作規範","createTime":"2018-09-08T11:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T12:55:36.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac4592f996c296cb0c34964efb7da69e92024dc","tid":810910,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180908/640_267da8792f24d2428228494423ff7e5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180908%2F640_267da8792f24d2428228494423ff7e5e.jpg&h=e047d5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國億萬富豪、特斯拉（Tesla）創辦人馬斯克（Elon Musk）惹「麻煩」！他前天在一個現場直播的播客（podcast）訪問中吸食大麻，此舉可能為他帶來麻煩。馬斯克創辦的SpaceX向美國空軍提供服務，獲安全審批（security clearance），可以接觸相關的機密資料，而政府禁止相關人士吸食大麻，故空軍已就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克前天接受支持大麻合法化的笑匠喬羅根（Joe Rogan）訪問，期間Rogan把一根含有大麻和煙草的煙遞給馬斯克，他不但當場試抽，並承認從前也曾抽過一次。Rogan說「因為股東（會關注），你也許不該抽。」馬斯克反駁道：「這是合法的，對吧？」當時節目在大麻合法的加州錄製。<br />\n喬羅根的節目《The Joe Rogan Experience》是美國最受歡迎的播客之一，節目播出後5小時，在YouTube的瀏覽量已達45萬次，其YouTube頻道更有320萬人訂閱。<br />\n美國空軍承認關注事件，發言人在聲明中表示「我們需要時間來確定事實、以及處理這種情況的適當程序。」<br />\n此外，馬斯克抽大麻，或也違反了他創辦的集團的政策。因為他是以特斯拉執行長的身份接受訪問，節目期間喝酒和抽大麻，代表他「神智不清」（under the influence）工作。（國際中心／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180908/1426253/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180908%2F1426253%2F&d=Fc73ds4qqqpJJjdPsHF6JRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d4696188\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180908%2F1426253%2F&h=c9681cce\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180908/1426253/</a><br />\n<br />\n一開始仲以為空軍係指沽空 <br />\n<br />\n原來係真空軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0572b74c8d04f1139d229f5907a39a2d0c1302d2","tid":810910,"uid":102240,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"一開始仲以為空軍係指沽空 <br />\n<br />\n點解咁白痴都仲敢講？仲以為好幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365fa9133a832d9896c95b893394dec6017d463d","tid":810910,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0572b74c8d04f1139d229f5907a39a2d0c1302d2","tid":810910,"uid":102240,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"一開始仲以為空軍係指沽空 <br />\n<br />\n點解咁白痴都仲敢講？仲以為好幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:08:40.000Z","msg":"睇慣左d財經新聞咁講未詳細睇內文啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7def20bad1d1eeb2ad3c3fc62050092af332f4cb","tid":810910,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"佢係咪有份炒大麻股 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}